{
  "video_id": "KSYb6RbuOG0",
  "title": "Mark Blyth on Basic Income, Tax Havens, Automation and *Why Should We Work?*",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2580.0,
      "end_time": 5620.0,
      "text": "So I have a question on the technical disruption side."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5620.0,
      "end_time": 8770.0,
      "text": "I live in San Francisco, arguably the center"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8770.0,
      "end_time": 10570.0,
      "text": "of a lot of the disruption."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10570.0,
      "end_time": 14650.0,
      "text": "And technocrats in San Francisco, for the past year or two, have really"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14650.0,
      "end_time": 17529.0,
      "text": "gotten into this idea of guaranteed basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17529.0,
      "end_time": 20380.0,
      "text": "or mincome, as a possible solution to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20380.0,
      "end_time": 25720.0,
      "text": "And to me, it seems, at best, a band-aid, and at worst, the beginning of the dismantling"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25820.0,
      "end_time": 27580.0,
      "text": "of the social welfare state."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27580.0,
      "end_time": 31110.0,
      "text": "And I wondered if you had any of opinions about the feasibility or impact of a"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31110.0,
      "end_time": 32110.0,
      "text": "mincome policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32110.0,
      "end_time": 34710.0,
      "text": "So this is one of these ideas that have been--"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 34710.0,
      "end_time": 35710.0,
      "text": "Can I actually add to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35710.0,
      "end_time": 36710.0,
      "text": "Sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 36710.0,
      "end_time": 40100.0,
      "text": "Because I&#39;ve spent the last 18 months in the Bay Area too."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40100.0,
      "end_time": 43970.0,
      "text": "And at least the kind of community, the intellectual community around Stanford,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43970.0,
      "end_time": 47180.0,
      "text": "has this thing of \"this is really great that we actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 47180.0,
      "end_time": 48930.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t have enough work for labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48930.0,
      "end_time": 50700.0,
      "text": "Because none of us should work anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50700.0,
      "end_time": 55380.0,
      "text": "We should just take 10% off of the top 1%, distribute it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55400.0,
      "end_time": 58480.0,
      "text": "and everybody gets to do whatever they want with their time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58480.0,
      "end_time": 60379.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a terrible solution, if you could actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60380.0,
      "end_time": 61480.0,
      "text": "make it happen, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61540.0,
      "end_time": 62400.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 62400.0,
      "end_time": 65600.0,
      "text": "And so why should any of us work anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 65600.0,
      "end_time": 67380.0,
      "text": "If it&#39;s going to be a sharing economy, if everybody&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 67380.0,
      "end_time": 70399.0,
      "text": "going to be Uber and Air BnB?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 70400.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m really curious about this question and what you think about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74300.0,
      "end_time": 76640.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s radical and it&#39;s anti-capitalist, but it could work."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 76640.0,
      "end_time": 77800.0,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 77860.0,
      "end_time": 81980.0,
      "text": "I totally agree, but the problem&#39;s getting your hands on the cash, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81980.0,
      "end_time": 83980.0,
      "text": "So my favorite example for this that I"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83980.0,
      "end_time": 86440.0,
      "text": "like to give in talks where I bump into Republican audiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 89390.0,
      "text": "which is usually when I talk to financial conferences"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89390.0,
      "end_time": 92200.0,
      "text": "and things, is to say, \"so how many of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 92200.0,
      "end_time": 93240.0,
      "text": "voted for Mitt Romney?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93240.0,
      "end_time": 94929.0,
      "text": "And quite a few hands are going up."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 94930.0,
      "end_time": 95930.0,
      "text": "\"OK, why?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 95930.0,
      "end_time": 96930.0,
      "text": "And I don&#39;t mean this as a partisan thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 96930.0,
      "end_time": 98300.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t mean it as a fairness thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 98300.0,
      "end_time": 100880.0,
      "text": "What was Mitt Romney&#39;s effective tax rate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 100880.0,
      "end_time": 101880.0,
      "text": "9%."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 101880.0,
      "end_time": 104500.0,
      "text": "Because he only pays capital gains at 15%."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 104500.0,
      "end_time": 107710.0,
      "text": "And he basically has tax shelters and incorporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 107710.0,
      "end_time": 110500.0,
      "text": "in Delaware and Arizona and the Cayman Islands"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 110500.0,
      "end_time": 110780.0,
      "text": "and all the rest of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 110780.0,
      "end_time": 113220.0,
      "text": "And he basically pays about an $0.08 to $0.09 on the dollar."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 113380.0,
      "end_time": 114240.0,
      "text": "I pay $0.33."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 114300.0,
      "end_time": 117960.0,
      "text": "If you add up all my state and local, I&#39;m paying German rates of tax, but I&#39;m"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 118120.0,
      "end_time": 120240.0,
      "text": "getting-- what would I call it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 120240.0,
      "end_time": 122119.0,
      "text": "Third world public services."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 122300.0,
      "end_time": 125340.0,
      "text": "So I can&#39;t vote for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 125400.0,
      "end_time": 127140.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s just unfair."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 127740.0,
      "end_time": 128740.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a fairness question."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 128740.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131900.0,
      "text": "But it hasn&#39;t really become a political topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 131900.0,
      "end_time": 135140.0,
      "text": "Because if that becomes the issue, then you can make an argument for that"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 135140.0,
      "end_time": 137890.0,
      "text": "type of radical redistribution, which is essentially"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 137900.0,
      "end_time": 138620.0,
      "text": "\"pay your goddamn taxes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 138620.0,
      "end_time": 140350.0,
      "text": "And given that you&#39;ve got most of the money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 140350.0,
      "end_time": 141859.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t tell me you pay most of the taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 141860.0,
      "end_time": 144390.0,
      "text": "You do in volume terms, but you&#39;re cheating on the margin."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 144390.0,
      "end_time": 146700.0,
      "text": "You owe a hell of a lot more."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 146700.0,
      "end_time": 148600.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a wonderful book called Treasure Islands."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 148600.0,
      "end_time": 151569.0,
      "text": "And the estimate in that is if you go to all the tax havens where all the"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 151569.0,
      "end_time": 153970.0,
      "text": "Mitts in the world have all their cash stored, and this"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 153970.0,
      "end_time": 155200.0,
      "text": "is just those bits."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 155200.0,
      "end_time": 157421.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s other places, like art, warehousing, and all that sort"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 157421.0,
      "end_time": 159900.0,
      "text": "of stuff you can hide wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 159900.0,
      "end_time": 161209.0,
      "text": "$29 trillion."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 161209.0,
      "end_time": 165310.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll say that again-- $29 trillion."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 165310.0,
      "end_time": 168320.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a lot redistribution you could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 168320.0,
      "end_time": 172400.0,
      "text": "And all of that is basically money that people have avoided tax on."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 172400.0,
      "end_time": 177990.0,
      "text": "So if the Community Chest agreement is, \"you made it here, you pay your taxes,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 177990.0,
      "end_time": 179709.0,
      "text": "well, we&#39;re making it everywhere and we&#39;re not paying any taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 179709.0,
      "end_time": 182459.0,
      "text": "Hence Poland, Ireland and all that sort of stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 182460.0,
      "end_time": 186420.0,
      "text": "So you can see the beginning of movement on this, particular on the corporate side."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 186420.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s there."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 187360.0,
      "end_time": 188980.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s get to the heart of the matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 188980.0,
      "end_time": 189840.0,
      "text": "Because this is really it."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 189920.0,
      "end_time": 192790.0,
      "text": "Why should we work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 192900.0,
      "end_time": 196380.0,
      "text": "I often think that economists forget that the most basic thing you learn in"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 196380.0,
      "end_time": 198460.0,
      "text": "economics is the labor-leisure trade off."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 198460.0,
      "end_time": 202440.0,
      "text": "As we get richer as a society, we&#39;re meant to work less."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 202440.0,
      "end_time": 207880.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not meant to be more insecure, working for crappier wages more and more hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 208100.0,
      "end_time": 209859.0,
      "text": "So why is that happening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 209870.0,
      "end_time": 211739.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s actually about the property rights behind it."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 211739.0,
      "end_time": 213879.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s go to San Francisco for a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 213879.0,
      "end_time": 215239.0,
      "text": "Uber is fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 215240.0,
      "end_time": 217920.0,
      "text": "I think Uber is absolutely brilliant."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 217920.0,
      "end_time": 218920.0,
      "text": "I love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 218920.0,
      "end_time": 220980.0,
      "text": "I love the fact that when you need to get to the airport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 220980.0,
      "end_time": 222179.0,
      "text": "they actually show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 222180.0,
      "end_time": 225690.0,
      "text": "I love the fact that it doesn&#39;t smell like nine people who&#39;ve"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 225690.0,
      "end_time": 229510.0,
      "text": "been murdered in the back of this car before I get in it, which is your average"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 229510.0,
      "end_time": 230599.0,
      "text": "city taxi."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 230599.0,
      "end_time": 234170.0,
      "text": "And I love the fact that all even if these guys are"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 234170.0,
      "end_time": 237980.0,
      "text": "basically ripping off the drivers, a much larger proportion of what they&#39;re"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 237980.0,
      "end_time": 240209.0,
      "text": "actually earning goes to them than rather it goes straight"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 240209.0,
      "end_time": 244230.0,
      "text": "to medallion holder who holds the license that&#39;s basically"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 244230.0,
      "end_time": 247170.0,
      "text": "a money pump from basically poor immigrants"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 247170.0,
      "end_time": 249540.0,
      "text": "who are earning an equivalent of less than minimum wage in tips."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 249540.0,
      "end_time": 250929.0,
      "text": "So I love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 250930.0,
      "end_time": 251930.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s great."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 251930.0,
      "end_time": 254620.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say Uber gets driverless cars sorted out."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 254620.0,
      "end_time": 259470.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll eliminate 8 million jobs in the United States like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 259470.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262729.0,
      "text": "Now, unless you&#39;re going to give them some kind of compensation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 262729.0,
      "end_time": 266808.0,
      "text": "a basic income or anything like that, what exactly do you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266809.0,
      "end_time": 269990.0,
      "text": "Now, this is where it gets more into the ethics of capitalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 269990.0,
      "end_time": 272229.0,
      "text": "because essentially we have a system that"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 272229.0,
      "end_time": 273419.0,
      "text": "says you need to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 273419.0,
      "end_time": 274930.0,
      "text": "Everybody needs to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 274930.0,
      "end_time": 277560.0,
      "text": "But what if you don&#39;t need them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 277560.0,
      "end_time": 279790.0,
      "text": "And this is a way bigger problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 279790.0,
      "end_time": 281639.0,
      "text": "Because all the returns go to the guys at Uber."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 281639.0,
      "end_time": 286539.0,
      "text": "All the returns go to the guys at Whatsapp, whoever gets robotics sorted out, all"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 286539.0,
      "end_time": 288120.0,
      "text": "the returns goes to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 288120.0,
      "end_time": 291539.0,
      "text": "That 1% is going to become basically an enormous chunk"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 291539.0,
      "end_time": 292539.0,
      "text": "of national wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 292539.0,
      "end_time": 294808.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to go to increasingly fewer people."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 294809.0,
      "end_time": 299539.0,
      "text": "Now, what we tend to do in those situations is we bust up the firms."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 299539.0,
      "end_time": 301669.0,
      "text": "So go back to the 19th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 301669.0,
      "end_time": 304490.0,
      "text": "Go back to the early 20th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 304500.0,
      "end_time": 305500.0,
      "text": "Anti-trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 305500.0,
      "end_time": 307309.0,
      "text": "Even in the &#39;70s, Bell, telecoms, the whole lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 307309.0,
      "end_time": 310479.0,
      "text": "When it gets too concentrated, when the returns are going"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 310479.0,
      "end_time": 314550.0,
      "text": "all one way, we tend to step in and actually break up the firms, redistribute the"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 314550.0,
      "end_time": 315810.0,
      "text": "property rights, whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 315810.0,
      "end_time": 317330.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what you really need to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 317330.0,
      "end_time": 320900.0,
      "text": "You need to democratize the returns to robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 320900.0,
      "end_time": 323409.0,
      "text": "If you do that, then it&#39;s sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 323409.0,
      "end_time": 325700.0,
      "text": "Because I wouldn&#39;t care if you replace me with a robot"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 325700.0,
      "end_time": 327650.0,
      "text": "if I got to go fishing instead."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 327650.0,
      "end_time": 328650.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 328650.0,
      "end_time": 329650.0,
      "text": "That would be fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 329650.0,
      "end_time": 332590.0,
      "text": "And There&#39;s still a lot of things-- forget the hype-- that robots simply"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 332590.0,
      "end_time": 333590.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t do."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 333590.0,
      "end_time": 336500.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s the fastest growing job in the United States?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 337940.0,
      "end_time": 339980.0,
      "text": "Elder care nurse."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 339990.0,
      "end_time": 343409.0,
      "text": "Would you trust a robot to lift your nanna a bit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 343409.0,
      "end_time": 345270.0,
      "text": "Not going to happen, is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 345270.0,
      "end_time": 346558.0,
      "text": "Not in a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 346559.0,
      "end_time": 349270.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s still a lot of actual human contact"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 349270.0,
      "end_time": 351609.0,
      "text": "jobs which really can&#39;t be technologically disrupted."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 351610.0,
      "end_time": 354150.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a hell of a lot that can be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 354150.0,
      "end_time": 356120.0,
      "text": "and they tend to be the people who are already"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 356120.0,
      "end_time": 357460.0,
      "text": "in that slice of the cake."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 357460.0,
      "end_time": 360308.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re pissed off, both the left and right parties."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 360309.0,
      "end_time": 363900.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;re raising exactly what the right issue-- why do we need to work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 363900.0,
      "end_time": 365539.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s more than basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 365539.0,
      "end_time": 371248.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually about we can produce-- we can produce a super mega surplus for"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 371249.0,
      "end_time": 373199.0,
      "text": "the planet with 10% of the population working."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 373199.0,
      "end_time": 375740.0,
      "text": "China can literally make everything that we need."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 375740.0,
      "end_time": 377599.0,
      "text": "Why are we bothering?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 377599.0,
      "end_time": 380290.0,
      "text": "Why does every country in the world need to make cars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 380290.0,
      "end_time": 382300.0,
      "text": "Why do we need to have so many different types,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 382300.0,
      "end_time": 385229.0,
      "text": "if ultimately you&#39;re just going to have a few self-driving models that will take"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 385229.0,
      "end_time": 386530.0,
      "text": "you from here to there, and you can call"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 386530.0,
      "end_time": 387530.0,
      "text": "them up on your phone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 387530.0,
      "end_time": 390609.0,
      "text": "So this is way bigger than just those issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 390610.0,
      "end_time": 391879.0,
      "text": "So they&#39;re exactly the right issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 391879.0,
      "end_time": 396490.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have an answer, but that&#39;s definitely what the question needs to be-- why do"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 396490.0,
      "end_time": 397490.0,
      "text": "we need to work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 397490.0,
      "end_time": 399680.0,
      "text": "I ask myself that every morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 399680.0,
      "end_time": 402169.0,
      "text": "Usually, when I&#39;ve been out the night before."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 402169.0,
      "end_time": 403459.0,
      "text": "\"Why do I need to work?\""
    }
  ]
}